Name: Kenneth Thornhill
Date: September 4, 2013
Card Name: Blessing
Card type: Defensive
Pick-up ability: Automatically equip this card. Previous equipment is returned to hand.
Equip: Cannot be unequipped manually.
Every turn, you draw a card.
If any player lands on you, they can equip Blessing to themselves and roll again to move.
Whenever Blessing is equipped to a player, that player draws 2 cards.
